! Tid2PNG

Screenshot Tiddler: Captures the currentTiddler as a PNG image

!! 1. Read Me

Usage: Click the {{$:/plugins/FSpark/TiddlerScreenshot/remix-icon/screenshot-2-line}} icon on the Tiddler toolbar to Captures the currentTiddler as a PNG image.

The best practice is to put the screenshot button in the "view toolbar", which is the default way. This prevents the screenshot from getting blurred due to accidental moves when taking the photo. (Or implement several assistive "screenshot" tools, such as keyboard shortcuts, floating menus, etc.)

It is recommended to use [[CPL|https://tw-cpl.netlify.app/]] for installation to get the latest version. Or you can drag [[$:/plugins/FSpark/tid2png]] into your wiki.

* code: https://github.com/tiddly-gittly/Tid2PNG
* demo: https://tiddly-gittly.github.io/Tid2PNG

